G'day Mate, just wanted to let you know that not everyone has the bandwidth for massive file sizes yet. I'm stuck using Australia's old copper wiring and struggle to download at more than 200kb/s. It can take me a whole day to download a single moving sometimes, 4k quality would be awesome I admit, but would take me all week to download. 

For now I'm happy with smaller file sizes even if I lose a little bit of that "BluRay Quality" admit, we all stare at these computer screens so much that our eyes are completely fucked, the picture could be pixelated like an old DOS game and we wouldn't be able to tell.
